                            <comment id="17827204" author="cstamas" created="Thu, 14 Mar 2024 18:46:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for report. So it seems &lt;em&gt;there is something fishy after all&lt;/em&gt;.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Until we figure what exactly, please see discussion on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MGPG-90&quot; title=&quot;Signing fails with 3.0.1: &amp;quot;no pinentry&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MGPG-90&quot;&gt;MGPG-90&lt;/a&gt; for some hints.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
